title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 1PM' game
maintext:
PORTLAND, Ore. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday afternoon’s drawing of the Oregon Lottery’s “Pick 4 1PM” game were:
4-2-2-8
(four, two, two, eight)
